Ciwon cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Ciwon cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki da Burtaniya suna tabbatar da cewa, yayin da a mataki dabam dabam dangane da kasar, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar daga Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da ƙungiyoyin kulawa masu tsanani ya kamata su kara shirye-shiryen su don haɓaka marasa lafiya tare da COVID-19 wanda zai buƙaci kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba 2019, an ba da rahoton rahoton rahoton rahoton cututtukan huhu da ba a sani ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton wakilin da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus a matsayin sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira ciwon numfashi mai tsanani na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A bayyane har zuwa yau shine cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da cutar mai sauƙi, watau kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari, COVID-19 ya zama cuta mafi tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari ke fuskantar cututtuka masu muhimmanci da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Rashin mutuwar marasa lafiya a asibiti saboda COVID-19 shine kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna tantance yanayin da ke cikin haɗarin COVID-19 a kowane ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki (EU / EEA) da Birtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na yanzu a ƙasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya da wannan a Italiya a lokacin 31 Janairu-15 Maris 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan kasar Sin, COVID-19 ya kara yaduwar yanki kuma yanayin cutar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu ya biyo baya na wannan kasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 annobar.
A cikin 5 Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. ya ba da rahoto kan farkon cututtukan COVID-19 na Turai da aka tabbatar bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO.
A cikin EU / EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton shari'o'in uku na farko a ranar 24 ga Janairun 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris 2020, an gano shari'ar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU / EEA da Birtaniya (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba 2019 da wannan rana sun haɗa da, an ba da rahoton mutane 39,768 da mutuwar mutane 1,727, tare da mutane 17,750 da mutuwar mutane 1,441 daga Italiya kawai.
Samun adadin haɗin gwiwa da kuma haɗarin cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta lamarin COVID-19 da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samu daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta ƙasa, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanai don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a EU / EEA da Birtaniya, da kuma kwatanta su da wannan a Italiya.
A matsayin dan wasan kwaikwayo na yawan lokuta masu aiki na COVID-19, mun lissafa tashin hankali na kwanaki 14 na lokuta na COVID-19, don haka la'akari da yanayin halitta na COVID-19, a kowane ƙasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya, a lokacin 1 Janairu - 15 Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin kararraki na kowane ƙasa da aka sanar a ranar 15 ga Maris 2020 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya na lokacin 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris 2020.
Hanyoyin COVID-19 a kasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya
Trends a cikin kwanaki 14 na tattalin arzikin cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya gabaɗaya bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Figura 1).
Ga EU / EEA da Birtaniya gabaɗaya, haɗarin COVID-19 ya fara haɓaka a kusa da 21 Fabrairu sannan ya karu sosai a kusa da 28 Fabrairu 2020 (Kayan abu).
Wannan galibi ya haifar da karuwa mai sauri a yawan lokuta da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashe EU / EEA da Birtaniya sun nuna irin wannan haɓaka yanayin haɗin gwiwa na COVID-19 (kayan abu).
Halin 2 ya nuna adadin cututtukan COVID-19, a ƙasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da wannan a Italiya na lokacin 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya bayyana cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da misalin karfe 8 na yamma, wasu kasashe 15 na EU / EEA da Birtaniya sun riga sun bayar da rahoton adadin mutane da aka yi kama da na Italiya makonni 3 kafin ko kasa.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin cututtukan COVID-19 da aka sanar da su sun karu da sauri a EU / EEA da Birtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin haɗarin haɗari na COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da daidaitawa a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Wannan yana faruwa ne duk da ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin amsoshin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na kasa, da kuma yiwuwar ma'anar shari'a daban-daban a ƙasashe da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, ciki har da gwajin kama.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da suka shafa a Italiya sun bayyana yanayin da kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da ƙungiyoyin kulawa masu tsanani a wadannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakarsu.
A halin yanzu ana samuwa a matakin EU / EEA bayanan 6% da 1%, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Ya kamata, duk da haka, a tattara su a cikin tsari don kara bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan lokuta da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Wani binciken da aka yi a 2010-11 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa akan samuwar kulawa mai tsanani da gado na tsaka-tsaki a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 gado da yawan jama'a 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 kulawa mai tsanani da gado mai tsaka-tsaki na kowane 100,000 na yawan jama'a a 2010-11).
Abubuwan da ke da alaƙa da samar da ikon kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowane ƙasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya na yawan lokuta na asibiti na COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin 90% na wucewa damar kula da lafiya, an bayar da su a cikin sabuntawar shida na kimanta haɗari mai sauri na ECDC akan COVID-19.
Tun da lokuta sun kasance har zuwa yau a wasu yankuna a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Birtaniya, da asibitoci da sassan kulawa masu tsanani yawanci suna bauta wa yawan jama'a na yanki, ya kamata ya fi kyau a samar da bayanai game da lokuta da gado masu tsanani a cikin Nomenclate na yanki na raka'a don kididdiga 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewa daga Italiya da kuma halin yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a EU / EEA da Birtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin watsawa na al'umma na ci gaba da SARS-CoV-2 da kuma ƙara yawan marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar wanda ke faruwa a yankunan Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin kimanta haɗari mai sauri na ECDC na kwanan nan, hangen nesa, m da kuma cikakken tsari yana da muhimmanci don jinkirin yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da sauyawa daga rikewa zuwa tsarin rage-rage, kamar yadda ake sa ran karuwar sauri a yawan lokuta bazai samar da masu yanke shawara da asibitoci da lokaci ya isa don fahimtar, karɓaɓɓensu, kar ku da kuma ku amsa.
Kimantawar haɗari mai sauri kuma ta lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai gajeren taga na dama a lokacin da kasashe suna da damar kara kara kokarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, yana yiwuwa cewa tsarin kiwon lafiya na wasu ƙasashe na EU / EEA zai fuskanci haɓaka marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ke haifar da mummunan cututtukan numfashi (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ya kamuwa da cutar sama da 80,000 a kasar Sin da sauran wuraren duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, ana iya watsa SARS-CoV-2 daga bukukuwa kuma yana haifar da alamun kama da irin wannan hanyar.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS amma ya fi watsawa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A mayar da martani ga yawan adadin wallafe-wallafen da ke haɓaka cututtuka, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙarin samar da sake dubawa da cikakken bincike na batun da ke haɓaka da sauri.
Za mu rufe asali game da cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin halittu, virology, ganowa, magani, ra'ayi, da kuma rigakafin cututtuka.
Kodayake tambayoyi da yawa har yanzu suna buƙatar amsoshin, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da cutar da ta yi barazana.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa mantawa ba ga duk China waɗanda aka bukaci su kasance a cikin gida don duk hutu da kuma makonni da yawa bayan barkewar cutar kwayar cutar.
Ciwon kwayar cutar yana da tasiri sosai ga coronavirus (CoV) wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a shekarar 2003; don haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta kira shi SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke da alaka da cutar CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta yadu da sauri a duk fadin kasar kuma zuwa kusan wasu 50 a duk faɗin duniya.
Tun daga ranar 2 ga watan Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da shari'o'in COVID-19 sama da 80,000, tare da fiye da marasa lafiya 40,000 da marasa lafiya 3,000 suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "maƙiyi na jama'a ne 1" kuma zai iya zama mafi iko fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an buga fiye da takardu 200 akan COVID-19 ciki har da kwayar cutar COVID-19, cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ganowa, da kuma magani tun bayan rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya ƙaddarin kwayar cutar da cutar cutar.
Wannan nazarin yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a sabuwar batun da sauri ke haɓaka batun.
Duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi kokarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da wani cuta da ke haifar da CoV, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar a 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya har zuwa yanzu game da rigakafin da tsinkaya na cutar, da kuma wasu tambayoyi da ake bukata har yanzu gaggawa.
An yi la'akari da CoVs a al'adance marasa cututtuka ga mutane, galibi suna haifar da kimanin 15% na sanyi na yau da kullun 4.
Duk da haka, a cikin wannan karni, mun haɗu da cututtukan cututtuka na ɗan adam sau biyu, wato, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da barkewa a farkon China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, bi da bi, kuma ba da daɗewa ba yadawa zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan cututtuka da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine cutar CoV ta uku a tarihin mutane.
