Asalin zoonotic na coronavirus na mutum
Maye gurbin da daidaitawa sun haifar da haɓakar coronavirus (CoVs) da masu karɓar su, ciki har da mutane, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san mutane biyu CoVs (HCoVs) suna haifar da rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun.
Barkewar cututtukan cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun sauya tsabar kudin don bayyana yadda mummunan cutar HCoV zai iya zama kuma yana barazanar rai.
Halin SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a karshen 2019 ya sake jawo CoVs cikin haske kuma ya yi mamakinmu tare da babban watsa shiri amma ya rage kwayoyin cuta idan aka kwatanta da 'yar'uwarta SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV ita ce zoonosis kuma fahimtar asalin zoonotic na HCoVs zai taimaka mana da kyau.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga bats inda ba su da patogenic.
Har ila yau, an san masu karɓar tallace-tallace na tsakiya na wasu HCoVs.
Gano masu karɓar dabbobi yana da tasiri kai tsaye a kan rigakafin cututtuka na ɗan adam.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-host a cikin dabbobi na iya samar da muhimmiyar fahimta game da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna gabatar da cikakken bayani game da ilimin HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin zoonotic da watsa nau'i-nau'i.
Muhimmanci, mun kwatanta da kuma bambanta daban-daban HCoVs daga hangen nesa na juyin halitta da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
A halin yanzu cutar CoV 2019 (COVID-19) ta tattauna a cikin wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma nuna bukatun don sauye-sauye masu karɓa na nasara da kuma tasirin juyin halitta na ƙwayoyin cuta akan tsananin cuta.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) na cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na kwayoyin RNA masu rufi, masu kyau, masu rufewa.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta suna dauke da manyan kwayoyin cuta na 26 zuwa 32 na kilobases daga cikin kwayoyin RNA an kira su "CoVs" saboda sunayensu na kambi a karkashin microscope na lantarki.
Tsarin tsari, CoVs suna da genomes marasa rarrabuwa waɗanda ke raba irin wannan ƙungiyar.
Kusan kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna dauke da manyan nau'ikan karatun bude (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara a cikin pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ana ci gaba da aiwatar da polyproteins don samar da furotin 16 marasa tsari, wanda aka tsara nsp1 <0x7E> 16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ORFs don furotin tsarin, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Har ila yau, an yi la'akari da wasu nau'i-nau'ikan nau'i-nau'i daban-daban na CoVs.
Dangane da bambanci a cikin jerin sunadarai, CoVs an rarraba su cikin tsara hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu beta-CoV halittar ya ƙunshi mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an raba shi zuwa jerin hudu (A, B, C da D).
