CoVs sun koma hasken rana saboda barkewar SARS-CoV-2 na kwanan nan.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin bukukuwan da sauran dabbobi ya canza sosai fahimtar mu game da muhimmancin asalin zoonotic da kuma tafkunan dabbobi na HCoVs a cikin watsawar ɗan adam.
Tabbatarwa mai mahimmanci ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da asalin bat kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar masu karɓar baƙi.
Tun da yake kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ya samo asali ne daga tuntuɓar tsakanin mutane da civets a kasuwanni, rufe kasuwanni da kisan civets a ciki zai iya kawo ƙarshen annobar SARS.
Ta hanyar wannan tunani, ya kamata a cire pangolins daga kasuwannin daji don hana yaduwar zoonotic, a la'akari da gano zuriyar pangolin beta-CoVs da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, ko da kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke watsawa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran mahaifa har yanzu za a bayyana a cikin binciken nan gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya kasance a cikin raƙuman dromedary na dogon lokaci.
Wadannan raƙuman suna zama muhimmin kayan aiki don sufuri da kuma babban tushen nama, madara, fata da kayayyakin fata ga mutanen gida.
An rarraba su a duk faɗin Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka ba zai yiwu a miƙa dukkan raƙuman don sarrafa MERS ba, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwannin dabbobin daji a kasar Sin don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da barkewar cutar MERS, ya kamata a dauki cikakken tsari don haɓaka ingantaccen alluran rigakafi da MERS-CoV ga raƙuman, tare da wasu matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta.
Kamar yadda ba za mu iya kawar da waɗannan kwayoyin cuta ba, sababbin kwayoyin halitta na iya fitowa don haifar da barkewar cutar.
Akwai nau'i-nau'i daban-daban na zoonotic CoVs suna yaduwa a cikin daji.
Musamman, coVs tare da yiwuwar zoonotic suna daban-daban.
Akwai da dama da yawa da wadannan zoonotic CoVs ke haɓaka da kuma recombine, wanda ya haifar da fitowar sababbin CoVs waɗanda suka fi watsawa da / ko kisa a cikin mutane a nan gaba.
Ya kamata a bar al'adun cin dabbobin daji a wasu wurare na kasar Sin don rage hulɗa da ba dole ba tsakanin mutane da dabbobi.
Tare da matsalolin SARS, MERS da COVID-19, ya kamata a kasance mafi shirye-shirye da shirye-shiryen amsawa.
A gaskiya ma, yawancin kwayoyin cuta sun wanzu a duniya na dogon lokaci.
Suna zaune a cikin tashoshin nasu har sai an sami damar zubar da ciki.
Kodayake ƙwayar cuta tana da fasali da yawa waɗanda ke son yaduwar kwayar cuta, ana iya rage damar da mutane su kasance tare da ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta da sauran nau'ikan namun daji idan mutane suna koyar da su bar su.
Ci gaba da kulawa a cikin mahaifa yana buƙatar fahimtar ilimin muhalli na CoVs da masu karɓar su na halitta, wanda zai kasance da amfani wajen hana watsawa daga dabba zuwa mutum da barkewar nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana zoonosis na kwayar cutar ita ce ga mutane su guje wa wuraren muhalli na tafki na ƙwayoyin zoonotic.
Yawancin sassa a cikin guntu na asalin zoonotic na SARS-CoV-2 har yanzu basu ɓace ba.
Na farko, idan bats ya watsa kwayar cutar kakanni na SARS-CoV-2 zuwa pangolins, zai zama mai sha'awar ganin a karkashin abin da yanayin bats da pangolins zasu iya raba wannan tsarin muhalli.
Na biyu, idan bats suna taka rawar kai tsaye a cikin watsawar ɗan adam, ya kamata a ƙayyade yadda mutane suka shiga tare da bats.
Na uku, idan mahaifa na uku yayi aiki a matsayin mai watsa shiri na gaskiya, yadda yake hulɗa da nau'ikan daban-daban ciki har da mutane, bats da pangolins dole ne a bayyana.
A ƙarshe, tun da yawancin mahaifa ciki har da dabbobi na gida na iya zama mai yiwuwa ga SARS-CoV-2, ya kamata a gudanar da sa ido da kamuwa da cutar gwaji.
Idan ya kasance bat, pangolin ko wani mahaifa, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko ƙwayoyin cuta na iyaye waɗanda suke kusan daidai ne za a gano su a cikin mahaifa na halitta a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a wannan yanki zai bayyana hanyar juyin juya hali na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da muhimman tasiri a rigakafin da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idojin bincike na COVID-19 "matsakaicin da ake tsammani" da "matsakaicin da aka tabbatar"
A ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta wallafa jagorancin shawara mai sauri don ganowa da maganin cutar sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV), kuma wannan jagora ya ba mu kwarewarmu kuma yayi nazari sosai don yaki da wannan annoba a duk duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabon cuta ne, iliminmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun ganewa da magani kuma ana sabuntawa.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wani sharhi game da jagorancinmu kuma muka bayar da sabbin ƙa'idodin bincike na "matsalar da ake tsammani" da "wanda aka tabbatar da shi" bisa ga sababbin hanyoyin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (sashe na bakwai) wanda kwamitin kiwon lafiya ta kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar kasar Sin ya bayar.
A watan Disamba 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu an kira shi a hukumance a matsayin cutar coronavirus na 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an kira kwayar cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris 2020, WHO ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaki da kamuwa da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta samar da jagorancin shawara mai sauri kuma an buga shi akan layi a cikin Binciken Likitoci na Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Wannan ya jawo hankalin da yawa tun lokacin da aka buga shi.
Ka lura duk da haka cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, iliminmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali dangane da binciken bincike da kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun bincike da magani suna ci gaba da sabuntawa.
Alal misali, jagoran bincike da magani na COVID-19 da kwamitin kiwon lafiya ta kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'a ta kasar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020, ya ba da jimillar bugu bakwai tare da wasu mahaloli ana canza su sosai.
Yanzu jagorancinmu ya karɓi sharhi ta Zhou et al., sun gabatar da shawara mai sauƙi ta kwarewa bisa kwarewar asibiti.
Ayyukan su sun kara sababbin shaida don jagorancinmu kuma sun yi nazari mai muhimmanci ga wannan annobar a duk duniya.
Muna godiya ga aikinsu mai muhimmanci kuma muna nuna godiya.
Duk da haka, aikinsu yana buƙatar sabuntawa bisa ga sababbin hanyoyin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (Trial na bakwai) da kuma nazarin kwanan nan.
Bisa ga bugu na bakwai (3 Maris 2020), don tabbatar da shari'ar da ake zargi ya buƙaci haɗa kowane abu ɗaya na tarihin annobar tare da abubuwa biyu na nuna asibiti don yin cikakken bincike, ko buƙatar saduwa da abubuwa uku na bayyanar asibiti idan ba tare da tarihin annoba ba:
Tarihin annoba: (1) tarihin tafiya ko zama a birnin Wuhan da ke kewaye da su, ko kuma wasu al'ummomi inda aka ruwaito cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin kamuwa da cutar; (2) tarihin tuntuɓar cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwaji mai kyau na nucleic acid); (3) tarihin tuntuwa da marasa lafiya da zazzabi ko alamun numfa daga birnin Wuhan da ke kewa <0xE2><0x89><0xA5> da kuma a cikin kwana, ko kuma a cikin kwana a cikin kwana biyu.
Nuna asibiti: (1) zazzabi da / ko alamun numfashi; (2) tare da siffofin hoto na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19; (3) jimlar ƙidayar kwayoyin jini da ke nuna al'ada, raguwa, ko raguwar ƙidayar limfocyte a farkon farawa.
Binciken da aka tabbatar da shari'ar ya kamata ya dogara ne akan shari'ar da ake zargi tare da kowane abu na kwayar cuta ko shaidar serology kamar haka: (1) Gwajin PCR na ainihin lokaci mai kyau don SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin kwayoyin halitta na kwayar cutar coronavirus da aka sani da sabon coronavirus.
Zamu iya ganin cewa gwajin PCR na hakikanin lokaci don nucleic acid a cikin hanyoyin numfashi ko samfurori na jini ya kara zuwa bugu na biyu (18 Janairu 2020) da na uku (22 Janairu 2020).
An ƙara gano samfurin jini a cikin bugu na hudu (27 Janairu 2020) da na biyar (8 Fabrairu 2020); sannan an ƙara shaidar serological zuwa bugu na bakwai.
Wadannan gyare-gyare bisa binciken sun ci gaba da aiki don neman mafi kyawun kayan ganewa na nucleic acid don gano sauri, da samfurori daga hanyoyin numfashi ciki har da samfurin jini, wanda ya kara samun samfurori daban-daban, kuma ya tallafawa kawo takamaiman sakamako mai kyau a cikin ƙa'idodin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin shaidar da ke tunatar da mu da gargadi tare da marasa lafiya marasa alama da marasa alama.
Saboda haka, zane-zane na Zhou et al. ya kamata a sabunta, kamar yadda suka rarraba mutumin ba tare da alamun asibiti ba a matsayin "ƙananan haɗari".
Har ila yau, dole ne a tabbatar da tsarin ƙididdiga a cikin ƙarin aikin asibiti da nazarin.
Don kammala, muna fatan ƙarin bayani kai tsaye ya zo kuma muna kira ga masu karatu su ba da sharhinsu.
Don gano "matsakaicin shari'a" da "matsakaicin da aka tabbatar," muna bayar da shawarar gano da kuma bin sabbin jagororin ƙasashensu.
Har ila yau, ƙungiyarmu za ta sabunta jagorancinmu don bayar da taimako.
