<0xC6><0x98>ungiyoyin haɗari na wurin aiki don COVID-19 sune aikace-aikacen tsaro na aiki da hanyoyin kiwon lafiya don kula da haɗari don rigakafin cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gudun haɗari da ya dace a wurin aiki ya dogara ne akan aikin aiki da aikin aiki, dangane da kimanta haɗari na tushen bayyanar, tsananin cututtuka a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan haɗari na ma'aikata guda ɗaya waɗanda zasu iya zama m ga kwangilar COVID-19.
A cewar Hukumar Tsaro da Kiwon Lafiya ta Amurka (OSHA), ƙananan ayyukan haɗari suna da ƙarancin haɗin aiki tare da jama'a da sauran abokan aiki, wanda ake ba da shawarar matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, ciki har da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna gida idan suna da rashin lafiya, da kuma kiyaye tsaftacewa na yau da kullum da kuma tsabtacewar yanayin aiki.
Ayyukan haɗari na matsakaicin haɗari sun haɗa da waɗanda ke buƙatar haɗin kai ko kusa da mutanen da ba a san su ba ko kuma ana zargin su da COVID-19, amma ana iya kamuwa da cutar saboda watsawar al'umma ko tafiya ta duniya.
Wannan ya haɗa da ma'aikata waɗanda ke hulɗa da jama'a kamar su a makarantu, yanayin aikin yawan jama'a, da wasu saitunan sayar da kayayyaki masu yawa.
Gudun haɗari ga wannan rukuni, ban da matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, sun haɗa da iska ta amfani da tace-tace na iska mai inganci, masu tsawa, da kuma samun kayan kariya na sirri da ke samuwa idan mutum da COVID-19 ya haɗu.
OSHA tana la'akari da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da wuraren shakatawa da aka fallasa ga mutumin da aka sani ko wanda ake zargi da COVID-19 a cikin haɗarin haɗari, wanda ke kara zuwa haɗarin haɗari mai girma idan ma'aikata suna yin hanyoyin samar da aerosol akan, ko tattara ko sarrafa samfurin daga, wanda aka sani ko wanda ake zarta da COVID-19.
Tsarin haɗari da ya dace da waɗannan ma'aikata sun haɗa da sarrafawa na injiniya kamar ɗakunan iska mara matsa lamba, da kayan aiki na sirri wanda ya dace da aikin aikin.
Barkewar COVID-19 na iya haifar da tasiri daban-daban a wurin aiki.
